\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset

Also, we have 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\psi\right\rangle =\sum_{\mathbf{b}}\left\langle \mathbf{b}|\psi\right\rangle \left|\mathbf{b}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

