 Therefore, given an observable, one can construct the aforesaid experiment
 to measure its value.
 We have, in effect, explicitly constructed the map 
\begin_inset Formula $e:\hat{\mathcal{H}}\to\mathcal{E}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

